707022f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ave. T - Van Sicklen St.
707022f-a.text:
Ave. T. at the N.E. corner of Van Sicklen Street. In the extreme right
background, is Lake Street; at the right foreground is Ave. T. The view
shows the church and rectory of St. Simon and St. Jude. (R.C.).
April 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
O REPPODUCTIONS.
